body:
## Release Notes

- Add CODEOWNERS and settings.yml files. @iphydf (#34)
- Migrate java dependencies to rules_jvm_external. @iphydf (#33)
- Release tox4j API 0.2.3. @iphydf (#32)
- Update annotations library in bazel as well. @iphydf (#31)
- Update intellij annotations @robinlinden (#30)
- Release jvm-toxcore-api v0.2.2. @iphydf (#29)
- Remove glob patterns that don't match anything. @iphydf (#28)
- Upgrade dependencies to their latest version where possible. @iphydf (#26)
- Fix build @robinlinden (#25)
- Enable .travis.yml check and use non-markdown license. @iphydf (#24)
- Remove unused dependency. @iphydf (#23)
- Remove direct scalatest dependency. @iphydf (#21)
- Update to next version of sbt-plugins. @iphydf (#20)
- Prepare for tox4j-api release 0.2.0. @iphydf (#19)
- Add a bazel test that ensures all our projects are GPL-3.0. @iphydf (#18)
- Revert "Add CORRECTION message type." @iphydf (#17)
- Relicense under GPLv3. @iphydf (#16)
- Avoid clashes with "build" directories on case-insensitive file systems. @iphydf (#15)
- Update to split audio/video bit rate setter functions. @iphydf (#14)
- Add CORRECTION message type. @iphydf (#13)
- Update to new sbt-plugins version, removing protobuf dependency. @iphydf (#12)
- Remove scalaz and scala-logging dependencies from the API. @iphydf (#11)
- Remove some old code for encoding/decoding values as bits. @iphydf (#10)
- Update protobuf version requirement to 3.5.0. @iphydf (#9)
- Update dependency versions in tox4j-api. @iphydf (#8)
- Use official markdown license for AGPLv3. @iphydf (#7)
- Only build master branch on Travis builds. @iphydf (#4)
- Add `localDiscoveryEnabled` to tox options. @iphydf (#6)
- Readme deplist @iphydf (#3)
- Update dependency versions. @iphydf (#2)
- Update for new toxencryptsave API in toxcore 0.1.0. @iphydf (#1)

## Maintenance (Grunt tasks)

- Set up sbt CI using GitHub Actions @robinlinden (#39)
- Don't try to resolve now-sunset bintray repositories @robinlinden (#38)
- Use toktok-stack 0.0.23 for cirrus builds. @iphydf (#37)
- Remove travis; add cirrus ci. @iphydf (#36)
